around it.

00:03:20.860 --> 00:03:28.059
The best way is a second person while you
fan it at the same time so all the steam is

00:03:28.059 --> 00:03:31.939
out as quickly as possible.

00:03:31.939 --> 00:03:37.129
Once it gets room temperature or body temperature,
that's the best temperature, then cover with

00:03:37.129 --> 00:03:38.230
a damp towel.

00:03:38.230 --> 00:03:42.209
Now it's ready to use for sushi and that's
how you make sushi rice.

